<para><ref refid="classwx_rich_message_dialog_1a6c2650439d36a09ee3292896861a5a16" kindref="member">IsCheckBoxChecked()</ref> can be called afterwards to retrieve the value of the check box if one was used. </para>        </detaileddescription>
